<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<%- include('head.ejs', { cssfile: 'index.css'}) %>

<body>
    <%- include('nav.ejs') %>
    <main>
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="m-auto container-lg row d-flex align-items-lg-center justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-10">
                    <div class="info">
                        <h1 class="story">Welcome to ezKey - Simplifying Visitor Access for Gated Communities<br>
                            <span>your
                                security is our
                                priority.</span>
                        </h1>
                        <div class="btnparent">
                            <button onclick="window.location.href = '/login'" type="button" class="btn greenbth">Login</button>
                            <button onclick="window.location.href = '/signup'" type="button" class="btn greenbth">Signup</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xg-6 col-lg-6">
                    <img class="" src="/img/2.png">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about container-md">
            <h2>About ezKey</h2>
            <p>At ezKey, we believe in enhancing security and convenience for gated communities. Our innovative app
                is designed to simplify and streamline the process of managing visitor access, making it easier for
                community dwellers to grant access to their guests while maintaining a secure environment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="keyfeatures">
            <h2 class="container-md m-auto" >Key Features</h2>
            <div class="container-md m-auto row g-3 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
                <div class="features col">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i>
                        <h4>Generate Temporary Access Codes</h4>
                        <p>Dwellers can easily generate time-bound access codes for visitors, ensuring maximum security.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features col">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield"></i>
                        <h4>Enhanced Security</h4>
                        <p>We prioritize your safety. ezKey employs robust encryption and authentication protocols to
                            protect your community's security.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features col">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i>
                        <h4>Real-time Notifications</h4>
                        <p>Receive instant notifications when your visitors arrive and access the community, giving you
                            peace of mind and the ability to keep track of who's entering.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features col">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
                        <h4>Visitor Logs</h4>
                        <p>Access detailed visitor logs, allowing you to review who has entered your community and when.
                            Keep track of past visits for added security.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features col">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-user-group"></i>
                        <h4>User-Friendly Interface</h4>
                        <p>Our app is designed to be intuitive and easy to use. With just a few taps, you can grant
                            access to your visitors and customize access parameters.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="features col">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-people-group"></i>
                        <h4>Community Directory</h4>
                        <p>Access a directory of community dwellers, making it simple to send access requests to your
                            neighbors.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="howitworks container-md ">
            <h2>How it works</h2>
            <p>
                <b>1.Registration:</b> Create your account and register your gated community.
                <br><b>2.Generate Access Codes:</b>  When you have a visitor, simply create a temporary access code and specify the duration of access.
                <br><b>3.Visitor Arrival:</b> Your visitors will receive the access code via the app, allowing them to enter the community during the specified time frame.
                <br><b>4.Stay Informed:</b> Receive notifications when your visitors arrive and access the community.
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="container-md ">
            <p>&copy; 2023 ezKey</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>